title: Sam Groth’s ambition to be premier meant articles on relationship with wife ‘not idle gossip’, News Corp claims
summary: A court has been informed that new privacy laws should not apply to stories published by the Herald Sun, which allege that the wife of a Victorian MP was underage when her relationship began. title: Garden shed of vaccine pioneer Edward Jenner added to heritage at risk register
summary: A shed where the father of immunology conducted trials for the first smallpox vaccine has been added to Historic England's list of protected sites. This inclusion is part of a broader expansion that features 138 new additions. The recognition highlights the significance of the site in medical history and scientific advancement.
